Title: Provides Tier 5 and 6 members of the New York state teachers' retirement system with the same service retirement pension factor as Tier 4
Summary: Provides Tier 5 and 6 members of the New York state teachers' retirement system with the same service retirement pension factor as Tier 4.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the retirement and social security law, in relation to providing Tier 5 and 6 members of the New York state teachers' retirement system with the same service retirement pension factor as Tier 4
